==Puranipen==
O mai purano janglo superbarodvib, [[Rondiniya]], phanglyas 750 milyonurya bersha palal. Yek kotor lesko ingerdyas andre bare kotora le Barodvipenge save si akana ando sudo. Aver kotora phanden de nevo thai kerden (ando [[Paleozoiko]]), o butjanglo superbarodvib [[Pangaea]]. Mai palal vi i Pangaea phanglyas ande dui superbarodvipturya, [[Laurasiya]] (nordutno) thai [[Gondwana]] (sudutno).
